sources.title: Sasq-Watch (Full Movie) Comedy, 2016
sources.description:
Nigel and Oscar have finally gotten funding for their Sasquatch expedition. But when their guide bails and rival Claus also joins the hunt, they must assemble a rag-tag crew of outdoorsmen to track down the undiscovered beast.

Director: Drew Hall
Writer: James Weldon
Stars: Paul Brittain, Adam Herschman, Christine Quinn
2016
